@startuml
title UC13 - Team State
[*] --> Draft : create
Draft --> Active : saved (valid)
Active --> Active : edit / sync update
Active --> Inactive : deactivate (referenced by match)
Inactive --> Active : reactivate
Draft --> [*] : delete (no references)
Inactive --> [*] : delete (no references)
note right of Inactive
  Không hard-delete team đang được Match tham chiếu.
end note
@enduml
